# --- Rust (general) ---
/target/
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk

# --- Cargo tooling ---
**/.cargo/.package-cache/
**/.cargo/registry/
**/.cargo/git/

# --- ESP-IDF / esp-idf-sys / embuild caches ---
**/.embuild/
**/.espressif/
**/build/
**/sdkconfig
**/sdkconfig.old
**/dependencies.lock

# --- CMake / Ninja ---
**/CMakeFiles/
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/cmake_install.cmake
**/build.ninja
**/.ninja_deps
**/.ninja_log

# --- Logs / temp ---
**/*.log
**/*.tmp
**/*.swp
**/*~

# --- OS / IDE ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/

# --- Python ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
.venv/

# --- Shared libs (si aparecen por builds locales) ---
**/*.so
**/*.dll
**/*.dylib

# --- Model artifacts ---
# Queremos subir el modelo binario del firmware:
!rust-ia/assets/model.bin
